{"type": "article", "id": 9319, "title": "线性吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-08T07:22:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235123vX4nPgYdeRBayIzc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t伦敦设计师 Michael Anastassiades 是个运用线条和光影的高手，他推出了一款线性吊灯，灯架全部是极为简单的线形结构，有的是直线，有的呈圆弧模样，有的则被设计成了不对称的 “U” 形，圆圆的灯轻巧地落在灯架上，形成和谐的光影和结构的平衡。Michael Anastassiades 的工作室创办于 1994 年，这是其<a href=\"http://studiomichaelanastassiades.com/\" target=\"_blank\">官方主页</a>，感兴趣的话，可以点击查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235119EPnpeYy4ULBND6cK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235119Isw8H6kBYAUW5SqV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235120OHJpjAQwmhbKR5VX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235120ouK0Jx82FBzNHGsb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235121vaBMUyAtLw0XKjZ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235121ZwFPK7hnMOYB3a08.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235121KUGc7THV2sL0814t.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235122Im4kuFHCNQOi192q.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235122u65im4dqDnBjhKCT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}